This paper proposes a novel technique for faster Neural Network training by approximating matrix multiplications and convolutions. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
